quran[7{c,v,t}:
2,275,"magar jo log sood khatay hain, aُ noon ka haal uss shakhs ka sa hota hai, jisay shetan ne chhoo kar bawla kar diya ho aur is haalat mein unn ke mubtala honay ki wajah yeh hai ke woh kehte hain :"" tijarat bhi to aakhir sood hi jaisi cheez hai "", halaank Allah ne tijarat ko halal kya hai aur sood ko haraam lehaza jis shakhs ko is ke Rab ki taraf se yeh nasihat puhanche aur aindah ke liye woh sood khori se baz aa jaye, to jo kuch woh pehlay kha chuka, so kha chuka, is ka maamla Allah ke hawalay hai aur jo iss hukum ke baad phir isi harkat ka iada kere, woh jahanumi hai, jahan woh hamesha rahay ga"
2,276,Allah sood ka muth maar deta hai aur sadqat ko nasho o numa deta hai aur Allah kisi nashukray bad amal ensaan ko pasand nahi karta
2,277,"haan, jo log imaan le ayen aur naik amal karen aur namaz qaim karen aurzakat den, unn ka ajar be shak un ke Rab ke paas hai aur un ke liye kisi khauf aur ranj ka mauqa nahi"
2,278,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, khuda se daro aur jo kuch tumhara sood logon par baqi reh gaya hai, usay chore do, agar waqai tum imaan laaye ho"
2,279,"lekin agar tum ne aisa nah kya, to aagah ho jao ke Allah aur uskay rasool ki taraf se tumahray khilaaf elaan jung hai ab bhi tauba kar lau ( aur sood chore do ) to apna asal sarmaya lainay ke tum haq daar ho nah tum zulm karo, nah tum par zulm kya jaye"
2,280,"tumhara qarz daar tang dast ho, to haath khilnay taq ussay mohlat do, aur jo sadqa kar do, to yeh tumahray liye ziyada behtar hai, agar tum samjhoo"
2,281,"is din ki ruswai o museebat se bachcho, jabkay tum Allah ki taraf wapas ho ge, wahan har shakhs ko is ki kamaai hui neki ya badi ka poora poora badla mil jaye ga aur kisi par zulm hargiz nah hoga"
